etails Grant Fisher earned bronze both in an excellent 10k field and a great 5k field.\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 844, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 765, \"end\": 777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grant_Fisher\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Grant Fisher\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grant_Fisher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grant_Fisher\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 790}, {\"ngram\": \"an excellent 10k field\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s now one of the world\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s best and, undoubtedly, the best-ever American distance runner.\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 939, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 914, \"end\": 922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997125309369572, \"rank\": 0.0002777117099453132, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 876}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His fitness is fantastic and his kick is now world-class.\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 997, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His fitness\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"his kick\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"world-class\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 996}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fisher\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s unprecedented success in the distance events on the track has changed the way the United States is perceived on the global stage.\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1091, \"end\": 1104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.8603966876409057, \"rank\": 0.16223789972138142, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://db