use\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yared Nuguse\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yared_Nuguse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yared_Nuguse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"1500m gold\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1879}, {\"ngram\": \"Cole Hocker\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1892}, {\"ngram\": \"their own way\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 1973}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He became the top American by defeating Nuguse.\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1994, \"end\": 2002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9993704990544048, \"rank\": 0.0006085163689961322, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nuguse\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2022}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He toppled the defending World Champion and self-proclaimed excellent kicker Josh Kerr.\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2111, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2101, \"end\": 2105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.7658143087026222, \"rank\": 0.3020860258785003, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the defending World Champion\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He beat one of the greatest of all time, Jakob Ingebrigtsen, handily.\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2181, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all time\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cole Hocker\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 1500m performance proved that he has the best kick in the world.\", \"from\": 2183, \"to\": 2263, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cole\", \"from\": 2183, \"to\": 2187}, {\"ngram\": \"Hoc